  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Before you start playing, you need to choose your team. Your team can
    consist of up to 3 members. Each of those members is going to have a position
    depending on where you place them (their position). On left is a backline position
    while on the right is a frontline position. The middle one is an all-rounder.\n\nYou
    can choose them by pressing the plus sign and then choosing your desired member.
    For each member, you can select up to two skills. Every member has 4 skills and
    some of them can be used from specific positions only, so make sure to read the
    member descriptions to know what they excel at. You also have to select at least
    one member and 1 skill for each of them. \n\nNote that playing without choosing
    all of the members and skills isn't recommended since it raises the difficulty
    drastically"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ea3febd2a652e944cbc6ba9ae7d35fed, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2390640544149086462, guid: ea3febd2a652e944cbc6ba9ae7d35fed, type: 2}
